<img alt width="20" height="20" src="https://forums.gauntlet-rpg.com/user_avatar/forums.gauntlet-rpg.com/gustavo_campanelli/40/633_2.png" class="avatar"> Gustavo_Campanelli:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>I once run a Dark Matter game (old Alternity system) where a bunch of ritualistic killers were murdering people with rituals inspired by Iron Maiden’s Powerslave</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>A not inconsiderable chunk of the cosmology behind my WIP setting came from hearing Powerslave <em>just</em> as I was about to fall asleep – the creepy moan at the start jolted me awake in terror, and my brain synthesized the lyrics into how some of the major hidden movers and shakers wound up conducting their reign of terror.</p>
<p>Anyway I wrote up a big ol’ Appendix N listing for Legacy of the Bieth <a href="https://lotbieth.blogspot.com/2018/10/legacy-of-bieth-appendix-n-revisited.html" rel="nofollow noopener">here</a>.</p>
          </blockquote>
